], "lanes_definition": {"source": "lanes", "entries": [{"entry_id": "n27143", "headword_ar": "طُنٌّ", "root": "Tn", "body": [{"kind": "italic_en", "text": "A bundle of reeds"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "canes,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(S, M, K,) or (so accord. to the Msb, but in the TA “ and ”)"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "of firewood:"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(Msb, TA:) thought by IDrd to be not genuine Arabic: and pronounced by the vulgar"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "Tin~", "text_ar": "طِنّ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ", with kesr: (TA:) n. un. with"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "p", "text_ar": "ة"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "; (K;) [i. e.] ↓"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "Tun~apN", "text_ar": "طُنَّةٌ", "orth_type": "arrow"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "signifies"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "a single reed"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "cane"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "[or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "piece of firewood"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "]"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "of a bundle:"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(S:) and the pl. is"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "A^aTonaAnN", "text_ar": "اَطْنَانٌ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ": (Msb:) [or,] accord. to AHn, a"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "Tun~", "text_ar": "طُنّ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "of reeds or canes, and of fresh branches, is"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "a"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "wryqp", "text_ar": "وريقة"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "[app. meaning a"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "leafy bundle"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "]"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "put together and bound round, and having flowers,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "blossoms, and plucked fruits put in the interior thereof."}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(TA.) ―         -b2-  And"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "A thing that is put between the two half-loads that are upon the sides of a beast."}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(AHeyth, K.) ―         -b3-  And The"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "stature"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "[of a man]: or, accord. to IAar, (TA,) the"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "body"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "of a man and of any animal: pl."}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "A^aTonaAnN", "text_ar": "اَطْنَانٌ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "and"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "TinaAnN", "text_ar": "طِنَانٌ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ": (K, TA:) whence, he says, the saying,"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "fulaAnN laA", "text_ar": "فُلَانٌ لَا"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "yaquwmu biTun~i nafosihi fakayofa bagayorihi", "text_ar": "يَقُومُ بِطُنِّ نَفْسِهِ فَكَيْفَ بَغَيْرِهِ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "["}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "Such a one will not rise with his own body: how then with another?"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "]: but accord. to IDrd, this is a saying of the vulgar; and he does not think it to be genuine Arabic. (TA.)       -A2-  See also"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "Tan~N", "text_ar": "طَنٌّ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "."}], "source_refs": ["S", "M", "K", "Msb", "TA"]}]}, "classical_definitions": null, "translations_attribution": {"model": "qwen36-35b-heretic", "generated_date": "2026-05-18", "pipeline_version": "words.translation.v1.spark"}}